trans-unit.source: Provides standard facilities for creating and managing a type-safe, ordered collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TableCell"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Brukes til standard for å opprette og administrere en type sikker, i samling <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TableCell"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: This collection supports standard zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: Denne samlingen støtter standard nullbasert indeksering.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableRow.Cells%2A> property provided by the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableRow> class returns a TableCellCollection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableRow.Cells%2A>egenskapen som er angitt av den <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableRow>klassen returnerer en TableCellCollection.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableRow> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableRow.Cells%2A>

trans-unit.source: Appends a specified <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TableCell"></xref> to the collection of table cells.
trans-unit.target: Tilføyer en angitt <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TableCell"> </xref> i samlingen i en tabell.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TableCell"></xref> to append to the collection of table cells.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TableCell"> </xref> skal føyes til samlingen i en tabell.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the preallocated collection item capacity for this collection.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir forhåndstilordnete samlingen elementet kapasiteten for denne samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The Capacity property represents the number of preallocated slots for storing items in this collection, whereas the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableCellCollection.Count%2A> property represents the actual number of items currently in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen kapasitet representerer antall forhåndstilordnete spor for lagring av elementene i samlingen, mens den <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableCellCollection.Count%2A>egenskapen representerer faktisk antall elementer i samlingen.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableCellCollection.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: The value of Capacity is always at least as large as the value of <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableCellCollection.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for kapasitet er alltid minst stor som verdien for <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableCellCollection.Count%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableCellCollection.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: When newly added collection items cause the collection count to exceed the collection capacity, the capacity is increased automatically to accommodate the newly added collection items.
trans-unit.target: Når nye Samlingselementer føre til at samlinger vil overskride samlingen kapasitet, kapasiteten økes automatisk å gi plass til nye Samlingselementer.

trans-unit.source: Increasing the collection capacity involves allocating additional collection slots, which incurs both performance and memory overhead.
trans-unit.target: Øke samlingen kapasiteten innebærer tildeling av flere samlingen spor, som medfører både ytelse og minneforbruk.

trans-unit.source: Use the Capacity property to optimize the collection capacity in cases where the total or maximum number of collection items is known in advance.
trans-unit.target: Bruke egenskapen for å optimalisere samling kapasiteten i tilfeller der totalt eller maksimalt antall Samlingselementer på forhånd er kjent.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableCellCollection.TrimToSize%2A> method to cause the collection capacity to equalize with the current collection count.
trans-unit.target: Bruk den <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableCellCollection.TrimToSize%2A>metoden vil føre til at samlingen kapasitet å fordele med gjeldende samlinger.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableCellCollection.TrimToSize%2A>

trans-unit.source: The preallocated collection item capacity for this collection.
trans-unit.target: Forhåndstilordnete samlingen element kapasitet for denne samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The default value is 8.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er 8.
